room_title: Escape room "Gangsters' Gamble" by Lake Geneva Clue Room in Lake Geneva
room_address: 772 W Main St, Lake Geneva, WI 53128
room_description: As a hotel employee, you’ve just been informed by the hotel owner, Hobart, that Al Capone, archenemy of Bugs Moran, has poisoned one of Bugs’ bootleg bottles of booze. It now falls upon you to reveal and remove the tainted hooch before Bugs arrives to pick up his stash. Succeed and all will be ducky. Fail and you’ll be taking the big sleep!
